458
00:56:10,130 --> 00:56:12,780
<i>Kde si teraz?</i>

459
00:56:21,750 --> 00:56:24,740
-Bolí to?
-Áno.

460
00:56:32,290 --> 00:56:35,020
Čo sa to tu deje?
Ma Roo!

461
00:56:35,020 --> 00:56:39,870
Zmlátil ho brat Jae Hee.

462
00:56:39,900 --> 00:56:44,170
